title: The God Who Wasnt There - Original Motion Picture Soundtrack - D
description:
Music from the 2005 documentary "The God Who Wasn't There" by DJ Madson

This is upbeat electronic dance music with a positive message from clear-thinking rationalists. Blasphemy is a victimless crime. No gods were harmed during the production of this album.
